{"text_id":80101,"tokens":["The"," question"," of"," whether"," students"," should"," be"," allowed"," to"," create"," their"," own"," summer"," assignments"," or"," if"," teachers"," should"," assign"," work"," to"," maintain"," their"," education"," during"," the"," break"," is"," a"," contentious"," one","."," Both"," approaches"," have"," their"," benefits"," and"," drawbacks",","," and"," a"," careful"," consideration"," of"," these"," factors"," is"," necessary"," to"," determine"," the"," most"," effective"," method","."," In"," this"," essay",","," I"," will"," argue"," that"," students"," should"," be"," allowed"," to"," create"," their"," own"," summer"," assignments",".","\n\n","On"," the"," one"," hand",","," having"," teachers"," assign"," work"," during"," the"," summer"," break"," can"," ensure"," that"," students"," maintain"," their"," education"," and"," do"," not"," experience"," the"," \"","summer"," slide",",\""," a"," phenomenon"," where"," students"," lose"," academic"," skills"," over"," the"," summer"," months","."," Teachers"," can"," design"," assignments"," that"," align"," with"," the"," curriculum"," and"," reinforce"," concepts"," taught"," during"," the"," school"," year","."," This"," method"," also"," ensures"," that"," all"," students"," are"," completing"," similar"," work",","," making"," it"," easier"," for"," teachers"," to"," assess"," and"," track"," student"," progress",".","\n\n","However",","," this"," approach"," also"," has"," its"," drawbacks","."," For"," one",","," assigning"," summer"," work"," can"," be"," a"," source"," of"," stress"," and"," anxiety"," for"," students",","," who"," may"," already"," be"," feeling"," burned"," out"," from"," the"," school"," year","."," Additionally",","," students"," may"," not"," be"," as"," motivated"," to"," complete"," teacher","-","assigned"," work",","," as"," it"," may"," not"," be"," as"," engaging"," or"," relevant"," to"," their"," interests","."," Furthermore",","," this"," method"," does"," not"," take"," into"," account"," the"," individual"," learning"," styles"," and"," needs"," of"," students",","," which"," can"," result"," in"," a"," one","-","size","-","fits","-","all"," approach"," that"," does"," not"," effectively"," support"," all"," students",".","\n\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," allowing"," students"," to"," create"," their"," own"," summer"," assignments"," can"," have"," numerous"," benefits","."," For"," one",","," students"," are"," more"," likely"," to"," be"," motivated"," and"," engaged"," in"," work"," that"," they"," have"," chosen"," themselves","."," This"," can"," lead"," to"," a"," deeper"," and"," more"," meaningful"," learning"," experience",","," as"," students"," are"," able"," to"," explore"," topics"," that"," they"," are"," passionate"," about","."," Additionally",","," this"," approach"," allows"," for"," greater"," flexibility"," and"," individual","ization",","," as"," students"," can"," design"," assignments"," that"," align"," with"," their"," learning"," style"," and"," needs",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," allowing"," students"," to"," create"," their"," own"," summer"," assignments"," can"," also"," foster"," important"," skills"," such"," as"," self","-","directed"," learning",","," critical"," thinking",","," and"," creativity","."," Students"," must"," take"," ownership"," of"," their"," learning"," and"," make"," intentional"," choices"," about"," what"," and"," how"," they"," will"," learn","."," This"," can"," lead"," to"," a"," sense"," of"," empowerment"," and"," agency",","," as"," students"," realize"," that"," they"," have"," the"," ability"," to"," direct"," their"," own"," education",".","\n\n","However",","," this"," approach"," also"," has"," its"," drawbacks","."," For"," one",","," it"," requires"," a"," significant"," amount"," of"," trust"," and"," responsibility"," on"," the"," part"," of"," the"," students","."," Students"," must"," be"," able"," to"," independently"," manage"," their"," time"," and"," complete"," the"," work"," without"," constant"," supervision","."," Additionally",","," there"," is"," a"," risk"," that"," students"," may"," choose"," assignments"," that"," are"," not"," academically"," rigorous"," or"," aligned"," with"," the"," curriculum",".","\n\n","Despite"," these"," potential"," drawbacks",","," I"," believe"," that"," the"," benefits"," of"," allowing"," students"," to"," create"," their"," own"," summer"," assignments"," outweigh"," the"," drawbacks","."," By"," empowering"," students"," to"," take"," ownership"," of"," their"," learning",","," we"," can"," foster"," a"," sense"," of"," agency"," and"," engagement"," that"," can"," lead"," to"," deeper"," and"," more"," meaningful"," learning"," experiences",".","\n\n","To"," ensure"," that"," students"," are"," completing"," academically"," rigorous"," and"," relevant"," work",","," schools"," can"," provide"," guidelines"," and"," resources"," to"," support"," students"," in"," the"," assignment"," creation"," process","."," For"," example",","," schools"," can"," provide"," a"," list"," of"," approved"," resources"," or"," suggest"," specific"," topics"," that"," align"," with"," the"," curriculum","."," Additionally",","," schools"," can"," require"," students"," to"," submit"," a"," proposal"," or"," plan"," for"," their"," assignments",","," which"," can"," be"," reviewed"," and"," approved"," by"," a"," teacher",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," question"," of"," whether"," students"," should"," be"," allowed"," to"," create"," their"," own"," summer"," assignments"," or"," if"," teachers"," should"," assign"," work"," during"," the"," summer"," break"," is"," a"," complex"," one","."," While"," there"," are"," benefits"," to"," having"," teachers"," assign"," work",","," I"," argue"," that"," allowing"," students"," to"," create"," their"," own"," summer"," assignments"," is"," the"," superior"," approach","."," This"," method"," fosters"," engagement",","," motivation",","," and"," ownership"," of"," learning",","," while"," also"," promoting"," important"," skills"," such"," as"," self","-","directed"," learning",","," critical"," thinking",","," and"," creativity","."," By"," providing"," guidelines"," and"," resources"," to"," support"," students"," in"," the"," assignment"," creation"," process",","," schools"," can"," ensure"," that"," students"," are"," completing"," academically"," rigorous"," and"," relevant"," work","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}